
Release 0.2.0 (future):
	* added cursor support
	* added initial(!) support incremental screen processing.
	* added timing algorithm for capturing properly around slow host CPUs
	* implemented frame down scaling, so captury_config_t.scale now takes affect.
	* make use of the new codec, capseo, drop all other codecs

Release 0.1.0 (2007-02-16):
	* initial working version for capturing and encoding video data
